Topic: SDT (Self Description Test) 🧠✨

👉 This is the only test where you directly talk about yourself
👉 No tricks, no speed → only HONESTY + CLARITY

1️⃣ What is SDT?

You have to write 5 short paragraphs:

1️⃣ Parents’ opinion about you
2️⃣ Teachers’ opinion
3️⃣ Friends’ opinion
4️⃣ Your own opinion
5️⃣ Qualities you want to improve

⏱️ Time: ~15 minutes

2️⃣ What SSB Checks

They compare your SDT with:

TAT stories
WAT responses
SRT answers
Interview

👉 They check CONSISTENCY

💥 If mismatch → Rejection

3️⃣ How to Write SDT (Correct Way)
🔹 1. Parents’ Opinion

👉 Focus:

Responsibility
Discipline
Behavior at home

✅ Example:
“My parents consider me responsible and disciplined. They appreciate my honesty and support in family matters. They suggest I should improve time management.”

🔹 2. Teachers’ Opinion

👉 Focus:

Academics
Discipline
Participation

✅ Example:
“My teachers find me attentive and hardworking. They appreciate my interest in learning and participation in class. They advise me to improve consistency.”

🔹 3. Friends’ Opinion

👉 Focus:

Social nature
Teamwork
Trust

✅ Example:
“My friends see me as supportive and reliable. They like my positive attitude and teamwork. They suggest I should be more confident in taking initiative.”

🔹 4. Self Opinion

👉 Be honest (strength + weakness)

✅ Example:
“I see myself as a determined and positive person. I handle challenges calmly and try to learn from mistakes. I am working on improving my confidence and communication.”

🔹 5. Improvement Areas (VERY IMPORTANT)

👉 Don’t write fake weakness
👉 Show real + improvable

✅ Example:
“I want to improve my time management, communication skills, and physical fitness through regular practice.”

🧠 GOLDEN RULES

✅ Be honest
✅ Keep it simple & real
✅ Show balanced personality
✅ Mention improvement areas

4️⃣ Common Mistakes

❌ Writing perfect/fake personality
❌ No weaknesses mentioned
❌ Copy-paste type answers
❌ Too long paragraphs
❌ Mismatch with other tests

5️⃣ PRO STRATEGY (SELECTION SECRET)

👉 Show:

Awareness of yourself
Willingness to improve
Real-life personality

💥 SSB selects trainable candidates, not perfect ones

6️⃣ Practice Task (VERY IMPORTANT)

Write your own:

1️⃣ Parents’ opinion
2️⃣ Teachers’ opinion
3️⃣ Friends’ opinion
4️⃣ Self opinion
5️⃣ Improvements

👉 Keep each 3–4 lines

🧠 SECRET TIP

👉 Interviewer will ask questions from SDT

Example:

“Why do your friends say you lack confidence?”
“How are you improving it?”

💥 So write only what you can justify

